%e A261354 a(1) = 31 since 31 is a prime, and prime(31)^2-2 = 127^2-2 = 16127 = prime(1877) with 1877 prime.
%t A261354 PQ[n_]:=PrimeQ[n]&&PrimeQ[PrimePi[n]]
%t A261354 f[k_]:=Prime[Prime[k]]^2-2
